ygData.subject: Deadly Launchpads

ygData.messageBody:
There's not usually any problem at the TP ring in
Dreadlands, its the getting to anywhere else from that point
that hard. The NEVER should be paired with either of
the Iceclad Ocean rings. Two words: snow dervishes.
Grubby little bastards that are always around the rings,
and usually jump those people just zoning in. As
advice, take the boat from North Ro until you can
teleport to at least the Eastern Wastes. (I am pretty sure
there's something you have to pick up from the rings
before you can actually fly there in
Velious).<br><br>Nukai Oakenwulf
